        <main class="w-full bg-[#FBF5F0] max-w-[1920px] px-[20px] md:px-[10px] lg:px-[190px] xl:px-[150px] m-auto">

            <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center py-[70px]">

                <div class="max-w-[1142px] w-full bg-white px-[10px] py-[10px] shadow-lg flex flex-col gap-[20px] text-justify">

                    <h1 class="font-[merriweather] text-[28px] text-[#000000]">Cancellation and Refund Policy</h1>
                  
                    <dl class="space-y-8">
                        <!-- Cancellation Policy -->
                        <div>
                          <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 font-[merriweather]">
                            1. Cancellation Policy
                          </dt>
                          <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                            You may cancel your order within 24 hours of placing it. If the order has not yet been processed or shipped, we will cancel the order and issue a full refund. If the order has already been shipped, the cancellation request will be treated as a return and you will be responsible for any applicable shipping costs.
                          </dd>
                        </div>
                  
                        <!-- Refund Policy -->
                        <div>
                          <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 font-[merriweather]">
                            2. Refund Policy
                          </dt>
                          <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                            We offer a 7-day refund policy for all eligible products. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, you may return the product within 7 days of receipt for a full refund. The product must be unused and in its original packaging. Refunds will be processed within 7 days of receiving the returned product. Please note that shipping fees are non-refundable.
                          </dd>
                        </div>
                  
                        <!-- Process for Returns -->
                        <div>
                          <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 font-[merriweather]">
                            3. Process for Returns
                          </dt>
                          <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                            To initiate a return, please contact our customer service team at <a href="mailto:info@geldix.in?subject=Return Request&body=Hello Geldix Pharmaceuticals" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600">info@geldix.in</a>. Provide your order number and the reason for the return. We will provide you with further instructions on how to return the product.
                          </dd>
                        </div>
                  
                        <!-- Non-Refundable Items -->
                        <div>
                          <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 font-[merriweather]">
                            4. Non-Refundable Items
                          </dt>
                          <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                            Certain items are non-refundable, including perishable goods, custom-made products, and items that have been used or altered. Please review the product description carefully before making a purchase.
                          </dd>
                        </div>
                  
                        <!-- Contact Information -->
                        <div>
                          <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 font-[merriweather]">
                            5. Contact Information
                          </dt>
                          <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                            If you have any questions about our Cancellation and Refund Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@geldix.in?subject=Question About Cancellation and Refund Policy&body=Hello Geldix Pharmaceuticals" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600">info@geldix.in</a> or visit our office at <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/7iSA9uBCFWpqXsrh8" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600">Shop 2, Katara Hills, Rapadia Village, 462043, Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India</a>.
                          </dd>
                        </div>
                    </dl>
                  
